caption: They are always  out of food, never properly stocked, there is hardly anything on the shelves, credit card machine is always broke and the management always makes excuses for such a poorly run business.  New management is needed!!!

The WORST customer service I have experienced in quite sometime. A young woman walking around food with hair to her shoulders and no hair net. Two employees 1. fixing personal food at the same counter that orders are being taken & another walking around eating. Music so loud that you cannot hear. Extremely poor environment that Govt workers patronize because of lack of choices.
